{"tid":711773,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【盡量多圖】LIVE 6日峴港膠遊首日有感而發","createTime":"2018-06-21T19:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T08:55:38.000Z","uid":81916,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9b5a61f8e8cb7442ab877d0d4a51fd092fcf8916","tid":711773,"uid":81916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T19:27:02.000Z","msg":"話說今日部機都FULL曬，全部都似D賓賓翻鄉下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n甚少有香港人，一落機就咋咋臨去VISA簽證櫃檯遞資料啦<br />\n咁本身就冇唱到散紙，全部都100美金張，比錢戈陣就俾佢食住上<br />\n找翻70美金另加80000盾俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁廢事嘈佢啦，拿拿林出境就算 <br />\n攞行李戈陣後面有幾檔賣SIM卡 7USD 7日無限，之前有爬文話出面賣5USD<br />\n結果一出去得翻EXCHANGE店<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即係CALL唔到GRAB<br />\n咁局住搭的士啦，都冇計，跟手行過去有過小朋友幫我搬個行李上車<br />\n我心諗仆街咁似大陸戈D呃搬運費檔既，點知原來係的士司機黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇個勢都係唔識英文，對部電話俾佢睇，就話10USD<br />\n冇計局住俾，之後開車途中心諗，屌，轉頭話冇USD又找盾俾我咪死<br />\n點知真係，仲要離譜到 俾20USD佢，佢找翻140000萬盾(約6USD)<br />\n咁我心入面就有點不忿，好似黎到任你地劏咁，我叫佢一齊入酒店唱<br />\n點知間酒店都係柒下柒下戈D黎，我話唱2張10USD，佢就話淨係可以唱翻盾<br />\n仲要個RATE低過出面一截，OKOK我認輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 怪自己唔唱定錢啦<br />\n如果巴打絲打未去過又想去，記得唱定碎銀啦<br />\n<br />\n18歲出黎做司機搵飯食，我敬佩你啊，小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/010835_1eccd06e7e7b8b420633bfa0fa328664.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F010835_1eccd06e7e7b8b420633bfa0fa328664.JPG&h=dd11a82f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入佐酒店提早CHECK IN，擺低佐行李都未夠11點，咁就有D肚子餓，想試下當地<br />\n出名既生牛河啦，但又唔想做ON9仔同酒店換，於是用翻僅有既盾，租佐部電單車<br />\n出去搵EXCHANGE，一撻著部車，你老尾，冇油既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n佢就叫我自己去入，望下GOOGLE MAP好似好近，但實則上真係好近<br />\n搵佐半個鐘都搵唔撚到，原來間油站有保護色兼好細間，得2部機，圖後補，冇影到<br />\n都係雞同鴨講，對4萬盾俾佢入就算入完都係一半多D<br />\n跟手係冇SIM卡冇網絡既情況下去搵EXCHANGE，<br />\n三十幾度飛緊車D風係熱嫁！！！一講先發現，冇搽到防曬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依嫁痛到仆街<br />\n戈陣錢又未唱錢，又冇SIM卡上網，最終係燈位度問佐個中學生，佢就隨手一指<br />\n我就向戈戈方向去，幾經辛苦，終於搵到間EXCHANGE<br />\n原來越南係全體放飯的，咁撞岩食飯時間啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最快都要等到一點半，望下錶先12點半<br />\n可以點？繼續係咁兜下兜下囉，反正乜都冇PLAN到，真係好隨心<br />\n見到間好似幾好咖啡店，望下餐牌，哇，飲杯當地既越南咖啡先係2.8萬盾(約9HKD)<br />\n但我再望下荷包，飲杯咖啡既錢都冇，都係死佐條心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  柒住咁渣住架車走<br />\n不過放心，我轉頭唱完錢，一定會返黎試你既<br />\nKEEP住鳩兜佐好耐，終於1點半，咁岩翻去戈間EXCHZNGE途中，撿到有間BANK<br />\n唔諗啦，直接入去啦，等唔切啦，又餓又熱又曬，3重滋味，呢鑊真係飽曬<br />\n成功唱完錢，梗係要食D好野啦！！！<br />\n但係銀行行出黎，有點暈個身有又狂標汗，好唔舒服，於是好直接狗衝翻佐酒店<br />\n沖涼，跟手係訓著佐，可能尋晚興奮冇乜點訓，又加上早機既關係掛<br />\n但好快就餓醒佐，第一件事，係好想食生牛河，於是向呢個方向出發搵<br />\n搵佐大概半個鐘，都係搵唔到，好痴線啊，點解會咁嫁，路過間好打既超市<br />\n就不如食住乾糧再搵順手買埋日用品，一上到去個食蕉就叫我放個背囊入LOCKER，<br />\n可能我真係唔越南D規矩，入鄉隨俗啦照做，最後買佐好多野飲，特別推介下<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/032301_94efc9661842de4656ced979a8d6b30b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F032301_94efc9661842de4656ced979a8d6b30b.JPG&h=98483bbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢枝真係好好飲，有果肉，有茶既澀味，偏甜佐小小咁多，真係好值得買，重點係6000盾一枝(約2蚊)，係香港買粒糖都買唔到，仲有枝無花果味未試<br />\nSHOPPING完真係頂唔順啦，乜狗屎垃圾都要食，我就兜翻去搵翻今日中午戈間咖啡店，<br />\n諗住應該有D特色小食可以試下，點知個妹妹拎個餐牌過黎，全部都係野飲，重要全越南文<br />\n丁點英文都冇，點識啊大佬，不過佢好醒目咁簡介翻D項目，有茶類，有咖啡，有滴漏咖啡，有沙冰，有果汁，唔記得影個MENU，我原本想試冰滴漏咖啡，佢可能覺得我會飲唔到，味偏濃，佢就推薦我試個手搖鮮奶咖啡，咁我由冇所謂照試啦，反正都係2.8萬盾，咖啡未上之前，佢會倒杯香茅茶過你，值得一讚，先淡後濃，強烈對比，刺激成個味蕾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以覺得特別夠味好飲<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/024314_91a2150d33ec0172bcc8c48df6de848d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F024314_91a2150d33ec0172bcc8c48df6de848d.JPG&h=377fb65a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n飲完就即刻埋單，因為野生發現對面有PHO食，二話不說就衝佐入，<br />\n鋪面好簡陋，冇乜特別，唔為意都未必察覺到<br />\n落完單冇耐，就第一時間拎曬D配菜俾你先，什麼金不換啊芽菜青檸戈D，十分齊全，<br />\n有D連見都未見過既都有<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/025358_f4aa17a627fbe132bf9a57c312ce84b6.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F025358_f4aa17a627fbe132bf9a57c312ce84b6.JPG&h=77b84893&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/025410_199f015099cbdf8c12fd30fe27cafb81.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F025410_199f015099cbdf8c12fd30fe27cafb81.JPG&h=b7ec302c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢碗係我咁大個仔食過最好食既河粉，第一啖就梗係試個湯先啦，越南粉湯為主嘛，<br />\n望落個湯好似好淡，清水咁，但事實上飲完杯咖啡咁濃烈既味，瞬間，係瞬間被雞湯既味蓋過曬，可想而知個湯有幾濃，圖上戈碗係牛+雞，牛肉既味同香港食開既牛，有D出入，本身肉質偏滑，味偏濃，配雞湯有另外一種層次，係香港食既生牛河係配牛湯，感覺上冇咁特出，雞肉係切薄片，應該係浸熟雪完之後用機刨出黎，佢皮同肉夾住既膏都係爽口的，認真特別，最後係個河粉，白滑概括曬一切，好新鮮！價錢你又估唔估到係幾多呢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/030837_2af8618fc116e9eaa985960d7e0cfaff.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F030837_2af8618fc116e9eaa985960d7e0cfaff.JPG&h=27ec903b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4.5萬盾(約16蚊港幣) 去邊度搵啊，不過黎緊仲有幾日，要試下其他店，但心郁郁好想<br />\n翻兜去食，好似上癮咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日去到呢度先。。夜已深<br />\n黎緊想試 法包 有冇巴打可以提供下地址<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6d34bf5b18c457bb2d3cdd276eb8cd380f2dcf","tid":711773,"uid":19991,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T23:27:52.000Z","msg":"爸打落地就比人瘋狂呃錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f98dc29a3e2959eb2e864d5dc5f5b77b736324","tid":711773,"uid":89595,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T23:30:01.000Z","msg":"除咗樓主on9<br />\n都唔知回咩好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2538e80bd01921d5a1e94824627872824a1cae01","tid":711773,"uid":6261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T02:34:20.000Z","msg":"做乜唔係機場唱$"},{"pid":"c928d050c146a2920673f8400ea18b44ab0b9302","tid":711773,"uid":6048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T02:51:58.000Z","msg":"我陣間都出發去峴港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abf2992e10a3015549add4370277e6f44fcbdd03","tid":711773,"uid":81916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b5f98dc29a3e2959eb2e864d5dc5f5b77b736324","tid":711773,"uid":89595,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T23:30:01.000Z","msg":"除咗樓主on9<br />\n都唔知回咩好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:06:50.000Z","msg":"未去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 資料收集又唔算齊"},{"pid":"c58c7aaee68cd8419f9518c7f34604805e21adc8","tid":711773,"uid":81916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2538e80bd01921d5a1e94824627872824a1cae01","tid":711773,"uid":6261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T02:34:20.000Z","msg":"做乜唔係機場唱$"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:08:19.000Z","msg":"成件事最柒沽碌就係呢樣"},{"pid":"f148d7b1917abb655085be4120adec3ee8738d28","tid":711773,"uid":81916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c928d050c146a2920673f8400ea18b44ab0b9302","tid":711773,"uid":6048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T02:51:58.000Z","msg":"我陣間都出發去峴港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:09:07.000Z","msg":"記得機場買sim卡同唱錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448c867fc20d1979d2ba17d5a92db0f24b75693b","tid":711773,"uid":45459,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:25:06.000Z","msg":"留名 幾好睇 睇樓主俾人當水魚"},{"pid":"f8714033a7d9ed72625f15a44130195c94b62fad","tid":711773,"uid":81916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"448c867fc20d1979d2ba17d5a92db0f24b75693b","tid":711773,"uid":45459,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:25:06.000Z","msg":"留名 幾好睇 睇樓主俾人當水魚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做一日水魚乜都够啦"},{"pid":"e0540fca14e055bfb21f9efa29e8ee2380fe8ce7","tid":711773,"uid":81916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:14:26.000Z","msg":"今朝訓醒就去佐嘆咖啡<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/140701_b7baa092ee27ccf3572e594e7c15bc00.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F140701_b7baa092ee27ccf3572e594e7c15bc00.png&h=8f811ca2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/140708_e295fb9ae66c1bfdcc5f7186a9f21524.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F140708_e295fb9ae66c1bfdcc5f7186a9f21524.png&h=af61734f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n杯椰子咖啡，冇冰的，見佢係個雪櫃拎佐舊雪到硬佐既椰漿加小小水ban到溶佐，再倒杯咖啡落去<br />\n以為唔凍會好難入口，但出乎意料<br />\n咖啡既滑配椰子香，超級match<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即刻有種好寫意既生活，好滿足<br />\n<br />\n依嫁去緊穩pho食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6690178479d765d826f30dde3af03cb6459f3e73","tid":711773,"uid":61903,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:29:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇到搭的士就冇睇了<br />\n明明係香港買電話卡去<br />\n到call grab就乜事都冇<br />\n深水埗越南7天無張40蚊有交易<br />\n我之前去一出機場50,000越南盾既路程<br />\n佢開我70萬盾 我廢9事理佢自己用grab"},{"pid":"8dffd6a3f350a80324b7565035f6bb4387c635a4","tid":711773,"uid":54965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T10:12:29.000Z","msg":"睇黎真係幾曬下啵 樓主晒到兩截色勁明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"945086c910d21642aacf7c74b5f1141a57310bf9","tid":711773,"uid":33843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"abf2992e10a3015549add4370277e6f44fcbdd03","tid":711773,"uid":81916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b5f98dc29a3e2959eb2e864d5dc5f5b77b736324","tid":711773,"uid":89595,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T23:30:01.000Z","msg":"除咗樓主on9<br />\n都唔知回咩好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:06:50.000Z","msg":"未去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 資料收集又唔算齊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:32:58.000Z","msg":"連登峴港post已經好充足 如果你去河內接近0資訊咁濟"},{"pid":"b863e8de9d0995026022e84896c5b01f3c9b3cf1","tid":711773,"uid":33843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:33:48.000Z","msg":"繼續吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad5c1049b69e156eca81f13456ccdcdc309525e4","tid":711773,"uid":39576,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T19:48:39.000Z","msg":"原來落地簽證會找番盾俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa46393e65a6ae9d48093f24de76fa27451d123","tid":711773,"uid":81916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T11:54:03.000Z","msg":"好啦，落雨冇地方去繼續係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n繼前日話去搵PHO食，係GOOGLE 推薦評分較高既鋪頭<br />\n叫 PHO CONTAINER<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/25/184731_8f0b712bc12fbd623d18d14881a564a5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F25%2F184731_8f0b712bc12fbd623d18d14881a564a5.JPG&h=ebb9c448&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/25/184732_21ac1412d81d702460172c9a06d61c94.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F25%2F184732_21ac1412d81d702460172c9a06d61c94.JPG&h=b5fa7d24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/25/184733_cc2eeb5a17c7e93c491020ec8e53efa7.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F25%2F184733_cc2eeb5a17c7e93c491020ec8e53efa7.JPG&h=c359d052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本上係做韓國人生意，事因峴港真係周街都泡菜仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n碗野冇戈日檔平民好食，不過不失，價錢稍為貴小小<br />\n係我心目中唔值戈個價，不過都係好平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食完之後之後時間尚早<br />\n諗住去五行山望望影下相，天氣極好冇理由浪費佐佢嫁<br />\nGoogle map啦，21世紀最偉大發明之一，<br />\n連旅遊書都唔洗買，set個位置，大概10分鐘車程<br />\n咁小弟都有渣電單車底，KEEP住 65～80 KM/H 大概有5分鐘度就到，<br />\n就到戈陣離遠都望到，真係山一座黎，唔算高，小型山峰仔<br />\n唔知咩念頭，即時取消佐上去既衝動，放棄呢個景點<br />\n同時又瞬間萌生佐去會安市既衝動，再黎Google map<br />\n大概30分鐘車程，應該不算太遠就狗衝起行，<br />\n一個人去旅行就有呢D好，話點就點<br />\n<br />\n同埋想講，越南本地人渣電單車好鐘意阻街，2條友平排行，霸2條線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係咁熟電單車操作真係唔建議自己試，因為你嗶柒佢都冇用，<br />\n佢唔會理你，你有你渣，佢有佢渣，跟手後面d車又嗶你，所以要保持冷靜<br />\n由於都係一條大直路，可以盡情比油飛<br />\n以為好爽？ 其實渣得越快，就越熱，個太陽太猛啦，就算有著長袖衫都係，<br />\n所以都係維持係70KM/H左右，大概16分鐘度就到佐會安市<br />\n<br />\n到佐之後第一時間覺得，呢個城鎮真係唔簡單，超級超級舊，有d似廢墟<br />\n等等我會出相既放心<br />\n樓唔高過3層，樓齡約莫估計80年起，唔係水泥牆身，係磚牆黎<br />\n比想像中要古老，不過保護得好好，極具當地民族風味！值得一去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢邊少泡菜仔，主要係洋腸天下，周不時見有旅遊巴車D遊客，<br />\n咁我就隨意搵個冇咁曬既地方停車，步行遊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/25/192454_d63181a80a891953ba56c8d047bd89bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F25%2F192454_d63181a80a891953ba56c8d047bd89bd.jpg&h=2ff1e92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對比翻香港真係好好天氣，同埋呢邊空氣環境超好<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/25/192606_ac88b95a0822a1ef9606b338fa4bde76.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F25%2F192606_ac88b95a0822a1ef9606b338fa4bde76.JPG&h=98b5f13d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好多遊客鍾意搭呢d人力車，咁熱既天氣，搭你遊一轉，血汗錢黎！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/25/192737_6848c2196f5590fb1b5fe939823cc824.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F25%2F192737_6848c2196f5590fb1b5fe939823cc824.jpg&h=43a7e46b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/25/193026_a1b7ce30df2e84d00384d4fb98a97ec4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F25%2F193026_a1b7ce30df2e84d00384d4fb98a97ec4.JPG&h=6e45c1b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n具有當地風味既建築，底層做生意，樓上就住宅<br />\n想入去試，不過應該還有更加特色的<br />\n鳩行到河邊<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/25/193901_23207076268cadd8603e26cb35123004.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F25%2F193901_23207076268cadd8603e26cb35123004.jpg&h=6be465de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢邊個天點睇都好正<br />\n最後我選擇佐一間中國風BAR<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/25/194119_224b8b48e21dfbec73ef16325bddb5ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F25%2F194119_224b8b48e21dfbec73ef16325bddb5ac.jpg&h=710d3cf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/25/194119_904572fc80ca8fb8e5b143d033099edf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F25%2F194119_904572fc80ca8fb8e5b143d033099edf.jpg&h=15e4a8ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/25/194119_4e1ca4ed4391c92fba290bf7ca6f5de1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F25%2F194119_4e1ca4ed4391c92fba290bf7ca6f5de1.jpg&h=5a437387&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/25/194120_9b7b28541f57153863cd6c4e70353849.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F25%2F194120_9b7b28541f57153863cd6c4e70353849.JPG&h=7d1a9054&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/25/194120_a723edde57dba607df97f05ab4b5ac18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F25%2F194120_a723edde57dba607df97f05ab4b5ac18.jpg&h=2b87f6f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/25/194120_d7e53c922b364ad0d92fe42ee95fb40a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F25%2F194120_d7e53c922b364ad0d92fe42ee95fb40a.jpg&h=9b151231&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/25/194120_587856fc7b6ad7f59a37767a10c7daeb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F25%2F194120_587856fc7b6ad7f59a37767a10c7daeb.jpg&h=6d535ed6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/25/194121_80533eb050d4afd58da1e9f82d6e9606.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F25%2F194121_80533eb050d4afd58da1e9f82d6e9606.jpg&h=9f7285cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n外面望入去好陰森恐怖，但又吸引到我行入去試<br />\n唔算大間，得張細檯仔同幾張凳仔<br />\n大約行佐個半鐘度，見遠距離有好大片烏雲飄緊過黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/25/194618_c2d3638e6d761ced27ad80ac5f072092.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F25%2F194618_c2d3638e6d761ced27ad80ac5f072092.JPG&h=7492a0c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拿拿林閃人啦，雖然天氣預告有話落雨，但霎時間話黎就黎，<br />\n邊夠你玩】，跟手憑記憶兜翻出大路，結果就行錯佐路，因為真係個個路口都一樣，<br />\n有時撞正單行，就又要兜多個圈，最後速逃啦<br />\n暴風雨前夕，真係天氣一下間降佐落黎，附近都幾空曠變得帶有點涼<br />\n結果係未落狗屎前逃離佐雨區，翻到五行山戈段路已經又要硬食個太陽<br />\n狗衝翻酒店沖涼，係呢邊，一日最少沖3次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee16c25739b09c7bc80c1fe5d4160d8e95460096","tid":711773,"uid":81916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8dffd6a3f350a80324b7565035f6bb4387c635a4","tid":711773,"uid":54965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T10:12:29.000Z","msg":"睇黎真係幾曬下啵 樓主晒到兩截色勁明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T11:54:36.000Z","msg":"個太陽有毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e07c4207d06efce19be0ba6ed3578d9cdf2a71b","tid":711773,"uid":81916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad5c1049b69e156eca81f13456ccdcdc309525e4","tid":711773,"uid":39576,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T19:48:39.000Z","msg":"原來落地簽證會找番盾俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T11:56:04.000Z","msg":"擺明睇人黎呃啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"979aee34dedb99766e84a230441babff1cf5db6c","tid":711773,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T12:32:11.000Z","msg":"其實峴港d的士我坐過咁多次<br />\n全部都跟錶架喎<br />\n最多食多你幾千盾"},{"pid":"fe8d128c07e8e654e27b7f1c45866d6bbd25e407","tid":711773,"uid":81916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"979aee34dedb99766e84a230441babff1cf5db6c","tid":711773,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T12:32:11.000Z","msg":"其實峴港d的士我坐過咁多次<br />\n全部都跟錶架喎<br />\n最多食多你幾千盾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T12:38:33.000Z","msg":"機場的士佢地夾埋做遊客生意玩一口價，唔係市區戈d掛 佢地連錶都唔打，直接冚𣄃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da687bd53e78ba6abaee070cba933e71b0728b6d","tid":711773,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"